seahorse 2.23.5
---------------

    * Fix importing keys from key servers [Mackenzie Morgan]
    * Factor out seahorse-plugins to a different module.
    * Add XDS drag and drop support. 
    * Remove gnome-vfs dependency and use gio instead.
